items.title: Humana is hiring to fill up to 100 new positions in Tempe
items.summary:
Humana Inc. is hiring up to 100 new, full-time employees this month in Arizona.  Humana is hiring for Pharmacy Technician and Customer Care Specialists positions. All roles will be at its Tempe call center, located at 7333 S. Hardy Drive, Suite 102 in Tempe. The company is hosting a Job Fair at the Tempe call center on Thursday, Sept. 28 from 8 a.m. to 1 p.m. and 4 to 6 p.m. Interviews will be conducted on-site!

The post Humana is hiring to fill up to 100 new positions in Tempe appeared first on AZ Big Media.
